'''Tretlin''' was a person who posted on the illegal [[Gundark's Gear Datalog]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Tretlin provided a comment on the [[COMPNOR stun blaster]], specifying that the item was ineffective except to frighten or stop fugitives or unwanted animals.

